A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Michael S. "Killer Mike" Render; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, Michael S. Render, widely known as "Killer Mike," is a Grammy
3 Award-winning artist, activist, and entrepreneur whose influence extends far beyond the
4 realm of music; and
5 WHEREAS, he has consistently used his platform to promote financial literacy, uplift
6 underserved communities, and advocate for meaningful policy change throughout the State
7 of Georgia and beyond; and
8 WHEREAS, Killer Mike serves as co-founder of Greenwood, a Black-owned digital banking
9 platform designed to address financial disparities and foster wealth-building opportunities
10 in historically marginalized communities; and
11 WHEREAS, beyond his economic advocacy, Killer Mike has further served as a powerful
12 voice for criminal justice reform, police accountability, voting rights, and prison reform,
13 using public platforms and media appearances to advance these critical causes; and
